To install the vimrc

create a ~/.vim/bundle/
git clone http://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
inside vim run :PluginInstall

To get the same terminal install urxvt-256color

To add widgets to your awesome window manager
git clone http://git.sysphere.org/vicious ~/.config/awesome/

copy default themes and create a custom themes inside your
awesome config location
cp -r /usr/local/share/awesome/themes ~/.config/awesome/

By default the rc.lua file will look for a theme
called themes/custom/theme.lua
